ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of SHERRY D. WIEBE of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year; and designation of SHERRY D.
